						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="document" href="/fr/Dossiers/Les-S-T-au-CTA/Publications/Message-in-a-Bottle-Learning-our-way-out-of-unsustainability" title="Message in a Bottle - Learning our way out of unsustainability" alt="document">Message in a Bottle - Learning our way out of unsustainability</a></h2>

	
	
	
	
					<p>








 




  
  

	
	<a href="/var/knowledge/storage/images/media/images/wageningenur3_medium/313627-1-eng-GB/WageningenUR3_medium.jpg" rel="lightbox[]" >	
	  </a>
	
		
			
	
  	






	 
  





	Discours d'investiture au poste de 'Professor of Social Learning and Sustainable Development' et à la chaire 'UNESCO' de l'Université de Wageningen (Pays-Bas), donné par Prof. Dr. Ir. Arjen E. J. Wals, le 27 mai 2010. (Discours en anglais.) </p>
							<p><span class="date">13/12/2010</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="document" href="/fr/Dossiers/Les-S-T-au-CTA/Publications/Message-in-a-Bottle-Learning-our-way-out-of-unsustainability">Read more...</a>
